trans-unit.source: JournalEntryUnifiedViewConverter merges navigation back history and navigation forward history (as exposed by <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Frame"></xref> or <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow"></xref>) into a single, [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie7-md.md)]-style navigation menu.
trans-unit.target: JournalEntryUnifiedViewConverter intercala histórico de navegação back e histórico de navegação direta (como exposta pelo <xref href="System.Windows.Controls.Frame"> </xref> ou <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow"> </xref>) numa única, [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie7-md.md)]-menu de navegação de estilo.

trans-unit.source: Both <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> and <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow> display navigation chrome that supports history navigation using the following mechanisms: - A button for navigating back one piece of content at a time.
trans-unit.target: Ambos <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>e <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>apresentar chrome de navegação que suporte a navegação histórico com os seguintes mecanismos:-um botão para navegar fazer uma cópia de uma peça de conteúdo de cada vez.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>

trans-unit.source: - A button for navigating forward one piece of content at a time.
trans-unit.target: -Um botão para navegar um peça direta de conteúdo de cada vez.

trans-unit.source: - An [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie7-md.md)]-style drop-down list that shows: - A combined list of up to nine items in back navigation history and up to nine items in forward navigation history.
trans-unit.target: -Um [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie7-md.md)]-estilo na lista pendente que mostra:-uma lista combinada de até nove itens anterior no histórico de navegação e até nove itens no histórico de navegação de avanço.

trans-unit.source: - The position of the current piece of content with respect to both back and forward navigation history.
trans-unit.target: -A posição da informação atual do conteúdo no que respeita à back e histórico de navegação de avanço.

trans-unit.source: The navigation history is stored by both <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow> and <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> in the following properties: **Back Navigation History**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: O histórico de navegação é armazenado pelo ambos <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>e <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>nas seguintes propriedades: **novamente histórico de navegação**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>

trans-unit.source: **Forward Navigation History**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: **Reencaminhar o histórico de navegação**: <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: To create the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie7-md.md)]-style drop-down list, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow> and <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> use JournalEntryUnifiedViewConverter to merge their individual back navigation history and forward navigation history into a single list of navigation history entries.
trans-unit.target: Para criar o [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie7-md.md)]-estilo na lista pendente, <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>e <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>utilizar JournalEntryUnifiedViewConverter para intercalar o respetivo histórico de navegação de back-individuais e reencaminhar o histórico de navegação numa única lista da navegação entradas do histórico.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>

trans-unit.source: The resulting list contains up to nine entries from back navigation history and up to nine entries from forward navigation history, plus an entry for the current content.
trans-unit.target: A lista resultante contém até nove entradas do histórico de navegação back e até nove entradas do histórico de navegação de avanço plus uma entrada para o conteúdo atual.

trans-unit.source: If you create custom navigation [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)], and need to provide an [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie7-md.md)]-style drop-down list, you can use JournalEntryUnifiedViewConverter to similar effect.
trans-unit.target: Se criar navegação personalizado [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]e tem de fornecer um [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ie7-md.md)]-estilo na lista pendente, pode utilizar JournalEntryUnifiedViewConverter para efeitos semelhantes.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntryUnifiedViewConverter"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância do <xref href="System.Windows.Navigation.JournalEntryUnifiedViewConverter"> </xref> classe.

trans-unit.source: Merges two navigation history stacks.
trans-unit.target: Intercala dois pilhas de histórico de navegação.

trans-unit.source: For <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>, the navigation stacks are available from the following properties: - <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A> - <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A> For <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, the navigation stacks are available from the following properties: - <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A> <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A> The two passed navigation stacks are combined into a single navigation stack that contains up to nine items from each navigation stack plus the current item.
trans-unit.target: Para <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>, pilhas de navegação estão disponíveis as seguintes propriedades:- <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A>- <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A>para <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, pilhas de navegação estão disponíveis as seguintes propriedades:- <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A><xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A>as duas pilhas de navegação transmitido são combinadas uma pilha de navegação único que contém itens até nove da pilha cada navegação mais ao item actual.</xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.ForwardStack%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow.BackStack%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.ForwardStack%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame.BackStack%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>
